__section__
default
__description__
Message body that is sent back to a user whenever a moderation from
this user is metamoderated.

Parameters:

	m2 = List of hashrefs containing the following keys:
		title	- Title of the discussion in which the moderated comment
			  appears.
		url	- URL of the discussion in question
		subj	- subject of moderated comment
		vote	- moderation vote on that comment

__title__
Metamoderation Message Body
__page__
messages
__lang__
en_US
__name__
msg_m2
__template__

[% vote_result = { '-1' => 'Unfair', '1' => 'Fair' } %]

[% IF msg.mode == 1 %]<P>[% END %]
Your moderations on the following messages have been metamoderated:

[% IF msg.mode == 1%]
<UL>
[% FOREACH m2item = m2 %]
	<LI> "[% m2item.subj %]" from the discussion 
	<A HREF="[% m2item.url %]">"[% m2item.title %]</A> which you moderated as
	<B>[% vote_result.${m2item.vote} %]</B>
[% END %]
</UL>
[% ELSE %]
[% FOREACH m2item = m2 -%]
	- "[% m2item.subj %]" from the discussion "[% m2item.title %]"
	which you moderated as [% vote_result.${m2item.vote} %]

[% END %]
[%- END -%]

[%- IF msg.mode == 1 %]<P>[% END %]Thank you for metamoderating.

__seclev__
500
